### API REST de Eventos - Exemplos de Requisições
### URL Base: http://localhost:8080

################################################################################
# USUÁRIOS
################################################################################

### Listar todos os usuários
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios
Accept: application/json

### Buscar usuário por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/1
Accept: application/json

### Criar novo usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao.silva@email.com"
}

### Criar outro usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria Santos",
  "email": "maria.santos@email.com"
}

### Criar mais um usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Pedro Costa",
  "email": "pedro.costa@email.com"
}

### Deletar usuário
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/1

################################################################################
# EVENTOS
################################################################################

### Listar todos os eventos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Accept: application/json

### Buscar evento por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/eventos/1
Accept: application/json

### Criar novo evento
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Workshop de Java",
  "descricao": "Aprenda Spring Boot do zero",
  "vagas": 20,
  "dataInicio": "2026-02-15T14:00:00",
  "dataFim": "2026-02-15T18:00:00"
}

### Criar outro evento
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Meetup de DevOps",
  "descricao": "Discussão sobre práticas de DevOps",
  "vagas": 30,
  "dataInicio": "2026-03-10T19:00:00",
  "dataFim": "2026-03-10T21:00:00"
}

### Criar mais um evento
POST http://localhost:8080/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Palestra sobre Microservices",
  "descricao": "Arquitetura de microservices na prática",
  "vagas": 50,
  "dataInicio": "2026-04-20T10:00:00",
  "dataFim": "2026-04-20T12:00:00"
}

### Atualizar evento
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/eventos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Workshop de Java - Edição Especial",
  "descricao": "Aprenda Spring Boot do zero - Edição especial com certificado",
  "vagas": 25,
  "dataInicio": "2026-02-15T14:00:00",
  "dataFim": "2026-02-15T18:00:00"
}

### Deletar evento
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/eventos/1

################################################################################
# INSCRIÇÕES
################################################################################

### Listar todas as inscrições
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Accept: application/json

### Listar inscrições por usuário
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes/usuario/1
Accept: application/json

### Listar inscrições por evento
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes/evento/1
Accept: application/json

### Criar nova inscrição (inscrever usuário 1 no evento 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuarioId": 1,
  "eventoId": 1
}

### Criar outra inscrição (inscrever usuário 2 no evento 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuarioId": 2,
  "eventoId": 1
}

### Criar mais uma inscrição (inscrever usuário 1 no evento 2)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuarioId": 1,
  "eventoId": 2
}

### Cancelar inscrição
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/inscricoes/1

